Terminus Solutions AWS Enterprise Architecture - Licensing

This project uses a multi-license approach to balance open collaboration with 
fair attribution and potential commercial opportunities.

Quick Summary

- Code: MIT License (use freely)
- Documentation: CC BY-SA 4.0 (attribute required)
- Diagrams/Designs: CC BY-SA 4.0 (attribute required)

Detailed Licensing

Code Files (MIT License)
The following are licensed under the MIT License (see LICENSE-CODE):
- All Terraform files (*.tf)
- All CloudFormation templates (*.yaml, *.json)
- All Python scripts (*.py)
- All shell scripts (*.sh)
- All configuration files

Documentation (CC BY-SA 4.0)
The following are licensed under Creative Commons BY-SA 4.0 (see LICENSE-DOCS):
- All Markdown files (*.md)
- All architecture decision records (ADRs)
- All diagrams and visual materials
- All troubleshooting guides
- All cost analysis documents
- All educational content

